A: The problem is that you are using nextElement() method which returns the next element as an Object and you are trying to assign it to a String. You should use nextToken() method which returns the next token as a String.
Here is the corrected code:
StringTokenizer strings = new StringTokenizer(line,",");
while (strings.hasMoreElements()) {
    cName[x] = strings.nextToken();
    cMascot[x] = strings.nextToken();
    cAlias[x] = strings.nextToken();
    x++;
}

Also, you should consider using a List instead of an array if you don't know the size beforehand. It would make your code cleaner and more flexible.

